738
00:58:26,107 --> 00:58:28,818
every man jack of them, Jack.

739
00:58:28,902 --> 00:58:31,571
Supposing a bit of water
has gone off, eh?

740
00:58:31,654 --> 00:58:33,948
Certainly one can never be too sure
