01:00:38,503 --> 01:00:41,756
Yes, of course you can.
Of course you can. You can.

778
01:00:41,798 --> 01:00:44,259
I'm a religious man myself,
you know.

779
01:00:44,301 --> 01:00:48,180
I believe in all that sort of thing
