865
01:07:19,820 --> 01:07:23,323
- What are you talking about?
- I'll tell you what I'm talking about.

866
01:07:23,407 --> 01:07:27,495
I'm going to pick up this red telephone,
which is connected to SAC...

867
01:07:27,579 --> 01:07:28,997
and I hope...

868
01:07:30,540 --> 01:07:32,709
Blast. Blast.

869
01:07:32,792 --> 01:07:36,797
Shot away, I expect, by one of your men
during this ridiculous fighting!

870
01:07:38,215 --> 01:07:40,259
Right.

871
01:07:40,342 --> 01:07:43,721
All right, Charlie, I've been
wasting too much time on you.

872
01:07:43,804 --> 01:07:47,601
I got a lot of wounded men outside.
Start walking.

873
01:08:09,875 --> 01:08:13,712
All the radio gear is out,
