874
01:08:13,796 --> 01:08:16,966
I think the auto-destruct mechanism
got hit and blew itself up.

875
01:08:21,471 --> 01:08:24,724
The fire is out.
The emergency power is on.

876
01:08:24,766 --> 01:08:28,270
Everything checks out all right.
