887
01:09:06,980 --> 01:09:08,982
The radio is gone,
and we're leaking fuel.

888
01:09:09,065 --> 01:09:12,485
And if we was flying any lower,
we'd need sleigh bells on this thing.

889
01:09:12,569 --> 01:09:15,573
But we got one little budge
on them Ruskies.

890
01:09:15,656 --> 01:09:17,575
At this height
they might harpoon us...

891
01:09:17,658 --> 01:09:20,745
