906
01:10:14,679 --> 01:10:16,890
I am General Ripper's
executive officer...

907
01:10:16,973 --> 01:10:19,935
so the president will want
to speak to me, won't he?

908
01:10:20,018 --> 01:10:23,731
There's a telephone box over there
and the line may be open.

909
01:10:23,815 --> 01:10:26,609
You wanna talk to
the President of the United States?

910
01:10:26,692 --> 01:10:29,570
I don't want to talk to him, Colonel,
I've got to talk to him.

911
01:10:29,612 --> 01:10:33,282
And if you don't put that gun away
