914
01:10:46,381 --> 01:10:50,009
Go ahead, try and get the President
of the United States on the phone.

915
01:10:52,679 --> 01:10:54,723
Try any preversions,
I'll blow your head off.

916
01:11:09,364 --> 01:11:12,200
Operator? This is
Group Captain Lionel Mandrake.

917
01:11:12,284 --> 01:11:14,328
I'm speaking from
Burpelson Air Force Base.

918
01:11:14,412 --> 01:11:18,291
Something urgent has come up and I want
you to place a person-to-person call...

919
01:11:18,374 --> 01:11:21,461
with President Merkin Muffley
in the Pentagon, Washington, D.C.

920
01:11:22,838 --> 01:11:26,049
Burpelson 3-9-1-8-0.

921
01:11:27,259 --> 01:11:32,306
No, I'm perfectly serious.
