what is going to happen to you...

937
01:12:41,550 --> 01:12:44,261
your frame outlook,
way of life and everything...

938
01:12:44,344 --> 01:12:48,890
when they learn you have obstructed
a phone call to the president?

939
01:12:48,932 --> 01:12:52,937
Can you imagine?
Shoot it off!

940
01:12:53,020 --> 01:12:56,649
Shoot with the gun! That's what
