941
01:12:56,732 --> 01:13:00,194
Okay, I'm gonna get
your money for you.

942
01:13:00,278 --> 01:13:04,408
But if you don't get the president on
the phone, you know what's gonna happen?

943
01:13:04,450 --> 01:13:08,078
You're gonna have to answer
to the Coca-Cola Company.

944
01:13:17,380 --> 01:13:20,300
This is SAC
Communications Control.

945
01:13:20,383 --> 01:13:23,763
The recall code O.p. E...

946
01:13:23,846 --> 01:13:25,806
