947
01:13:25,848 --> 01:13:30,771
by elements of
the 8-4-3 Bomb Wing.

948
01:13:30,812 --> 01:13:32,814
These are the details.

949
01:13:32,898 --> 01:13:37,444
Missions 12, 22, 30 and 38...

950
01:13:37,527 --> 01:13:41,115
are reported destroyed
by enemy action.

951
01:13:41,157 --> 01:13:45,787
All other missions have
acknowledged recall code.

952
01:13:45,828 --> 01:13:47,789
This is SAC Communications Control.

953
01:13:47,830 --> 01:13:49,499
Over and out.

