Animals could be bred
and slaughtered.

1143
01:29:02,505 --> 01:29:06,927
A quick survey would have to be made of
the available mine sites in the country.

1144
01:29:07,010 --> 01:29:10,805
But I would guess
that a dwelling space...

1145
01:29:10,847 --> 01:29:14,518
for several hundred thousand of
our people could easily be provided.

1146
01:29:14,601 --> 01:29:17,730
Well, I would hate
to have to decide...

1147
01:29:17,813 --> 01:29:20,691
who stays up and who goes down.

1148
01:29:20,775 --> 01:29:24,695
Well, that would not be
necessary, Mr. President.

1149
01:29:24,737 --> 01:29:27,616
It could easily be accomplished
with a computer.

1150
01:29:27,699 --> 01:29:29,993
And the computer could
be set and programmed...

1151
01:29:30,035 --> 01:29:33,121
