of necessary skills.

1154
01:29:39,003 --> 01:29:41,256
Of course, it would be
absolutely vital...

1155
01:29:41,339 --> 01:29:45,301
that our top government
and military men be included...

1156
01:29:45,385 --> 01:29:50,224
to foster and impart the required
principles of leadership and tradition.

1157
01:29:56,273 --> 01:29:59,192
Naturally, they would breed
prodigiously.

1158
01:29:59,234 --> 01:30:02,070
There would be much time
and little to do.

1159
01:30:03,655 --> 01:30:08,578
